canonical:
  title: 胡家務館次途中韻
  author: 金克己
  language: lzh
  text: 去家才一月茫若隔三年客路天低處鄕心日出邊病妻應自苦嬌子有誰憐學道元無累今朝忽慘然
  rtl: true
  vertical: true
lzh_formatted:
  title: 胡家務館次途中韻
  author: 金克己
  language: lzh
  text: 去家才一月。茫若隔三年。客路天低處。鄕心日出邊。病妻應自苦。嬌子有誰憐。學道元無累。今朝忽慘然。
korean:
  title: 호가무관 차 도중운
  author: 김극기
  language: kor
  text: |-
    집 떠난 지 겨우 한 달인데
    아득히 3년이나 된 것 같구나
    나그네 길은 하늘도 나직한 곳
    고향 생각은 해뜨는 저쪽
    병든 처녀는 혼자서 고생하리
    어여쁜 자식은 누가 거두어 주나
    도를 배워 원래 걸림이 없더니
    내 문득 오늘 아침에 마음 처량하구나
  url: https://db.itkc.or.kr/dir/item?itemId=BT#dir/node?dataId=ITKC_BT_1365A_0120_010_0380&viewSync=OT
  footnotes: []
english:
  title: At the Hujia Guesthouse, Following the Rhyme of the Road
  author: Kim Geuk-gi
  language: eng
  text: |-
    A month since I left home,
    yet it feels like three years have passed.
    On the traveler's path the sky hangs low,
    my thoughts of home rise with the distant sun.
    My ailing wife suffers alone there—
    who will care for my gentle child?
    I have learned that the Way requires nothing,
    yet this morning my heart suddenly breaks.
  footnotes:
    - The poem contrasts the Buddhist/Daoist philosophical principle of detachment ("the Way requires nothing") with the poet's inability to escape human attachment and grief, creating the tension that culminates in the final couplet's emotional collapse.
